        <li>Intensity-modulated radiation therapy (IMRT) </li>
        <li>Interstitial (brachytherapy) </li>
        <li>Anteroposterior/posteroanterior (AP/PA) photons </li>
        <li>PA + laterals + electron boost to inguinal lymph nodes </li>
        <li>4-field box </li>
        <li>Consideration of RT dose to primary </li>
        <li>Consideration of RT volume needed (pelvis, primary, medial and inguinal lymph nodes) </li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Chemotherapy
    <ul style="list-style-type: disc;">
        <li>Mitomycin </li>
        <li>Cisplatin </li>
        <li>5-fluorouracil </li>
    </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Combination therapy: RT and chemotherapy </li>
    <li>Routine post-treatment biopsy </li>
</ol></p>
